Author: DateCoin_support
Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: 💜 Nikita Anufriev, DateCoin CEO delivered a talk at Tokyo Blockchain Week  Nikita Anufriev, DateCoin CEO has delivered a talk at Tokyo Blockchain Week, where he shared an opinion on kindling interest to ICO and presented recent project updates.  'Nowadays ICO are not that popular any more. Less investors pick cryptoprojects’ opened his talk Nikita Anufriev, DateCoin CEO. ‘Statistics shows that the total funds raised last August dropped to $326M reaching minimal values since May, 2017. Just to compare, it amounted to $3 bln monthly earlier this year that means almost tenfold drop’.  According to Nikita Anufriev, the reason for such an outcome is simple. That is numerous scam projects failed to meet investors expectations. 'Thus, strict following Road Map and regular updates of investors are our top priorities’, emphasized DateCoin CEO. 'We respond all the concerns promptly, keep our investors updated about project development and try our best for them to feel safe’.  'Another reason for reduced interest to ICO is the dramatic price drop of Ethereum (from $1400 to $170 or 9 times) in less than a year. It correlates pretty well with the drop of total ICO monthly funding’, emphasizes Nikita Anufriev. According to him, one more reason is an enhanced privacy of crypto community.  “To revitalize ICO it is essential to create the products for crowds rather than for crypto enthusiasts’, says Nikita Anufriev. 'That is the primary goal  of DateCoin. Thus, our approach is tokens for people rather than tokens for tokens.  To confirm the vitality of this philosophy, DateCoin CEO referred to statistics. It indicates 180K+  tokens were used for in-app purchases since its implementation in MVP,  Denim for Android. Thus, the tokens are in high demand due to its transparent mechanics and benefits they provide (up to 50% off for in-app purchases). For tens or even hundreds of thousands of people, our project contributed in popularizing   crypto economics’, says Nikita Anufriev.  According to him DateCoin team is working hard to launch the app in Japan. For instance, the app has been redesigned completely, new features have been added (such as unique virtual gifts, audio messages and much more). To remove language barrier, an instantaneous translation in chats has been implemented. This list of upgrades is far from complete.  ‘What is even more important, these efforts target not only app launch at Japanese market,  but an increase in DateCoin users, finally resulting in token price rise’ summarizes Nikita Anufriev.  ▶️ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vZ5XhN598wM&feature=youtu.be  https://datecoin.io

Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: 👩Girls talk about their expectations from DateCoin and desirable features  DateCoin MVP audience increases gradually with girls being dominant users. We surveyed them to figure out partner preferences and desirable features to make matching even more convenient and efficient.  Survey results show that most of the girls are interested in LTR with mature men (65%). 21% of respondents desire a lover, 7% of girls need fun and another 7% are simply looking for somebody to chat with.  When picking a partner, 36% of girls pay attention to communication patterns, 34% care mostly for him to be handsome (being attractive, sleek, of a specific height and body type). Another 16% of respondents first examine the profile thoroughly (dating goals, interests, education, etc). Finally, 14% of girls pay attention to solvency indicators (luxury watches, cars, real estate, etc).  More than 70% of girls who use Denim, date men from the app regularly. From them the rate of girls who enjoy the dates is  4.5 times more compared those with negative experience.  60% of respondents value generosity and care, 20% are attracted by self-confidence and commitment, another 17% are looking for charisma and sense of humor. Less respondents ( 3%) indicate sex appeal and temperament as the key criteria for choosing a partner.  Girls are confident for the service to become better and even more convenient with intelligent algorithms implemented in order to ensure an ideal partner matching. Respondents prefer personal data to be more detailed, verification and ranking for men implemented.  DateCoin team highly appreciates survey participants and will work hard on app upgrade based on users suggestions.  🔺 Lean more about us here: https://datecoin.io

Author: DateCoin_support
Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: 💜 DateCoinShow launched on YouTube  On July 19, 2018 Nikita Anufriev went live and answered the questions of Japanese investors. The streaming lasted for more than an hour and attracted several tens of users.  Nikita Anufriev started from appreciation of investors who have believed in project and keep on supporting DateCoin. The team has recently done a great job and thus DTC token will soon be implemented in Denim app (project MVP). According to CEO, this solution is currently under test.  Nikita Anufriev  mentioned that a total of 123 964 924 DTC tokens have been sold. All the tokens were distributed among investors who submitted a request for token withdrawal at our website.  When answering the question about possible future token listing at various exchanges, Nikita Anufriev emphasized that the team members are currently negotiate with several Asian and European exchanges. In contrast with  expectations of team members and investors, token listing is slightly delayed due to recently adopted regulations of crypto currency market. At the same time DateCoin is targeting to reach sufficient trade volume after token in-app implementation.  Talking about token price drop at Yobit exchange, Nikita Anufriev emphasized that it is essential for token holders to pay attention not only to the price, but also to the trade volume. For instance, the token price could rise higher than that at ICO with 1BTC buy order only. ‘It clearly indicates that our investors believe in project and are not willing to sell their tokens’, Nikita Anufriev mentioned. ‘Product development is the key driver for token price rise and our first priority’.  Investors were also interested in following Road Map. Nikifa Anufriev has ensured them that the team meets the deadlines and is actively on the app for Japanese users. He has demonstrated a new design targeting local audience.  According to CEO, the in-depth market research has preceded.  Streaming audience was also concerned about unsold tokens in general and whether it to be burnt as mentioned in White Paper. Nikita Anufriev ensured them that it will be done as soon as token distribution process is over, specifically in late summer or early fall. The burning event is TBA and will for sure affect token price.  To conclude, Nikita Anufriev talked about the plans of regular online meetings with investors. It is worth mentioning that Yuto Abe and Emi Wada, the project advisors in Japan, have also participated in conversation. Interpretation to Japanese was made by Rio Agawa,  the long-term DateCoin supporter and friend.  https://datecoin.io

I spoke with Aventhe and he said that spreadsheet will be update today or tomorrow!  I really hope so, at the moment to anyone looking at the speadsheet it looks like either nobody is running your signature campaign, or you don't care at all and the project has been abandoned... If the spreadheed will not be updated as promised I think I will soon leave this campaign - at this point I am not even sure there is a campaign.  Here when in MID FEBRUARY we have discovered that while we were promoting the ICO the manager was in vacation for several weeks, not caring at all about the campaign I was promoting:  Quote from: RoccoSiffredi on February 12, 2018, 10:57:36 AM Quote from: RoccoSiffredi on January 24, 2018, 07:36:55 PM Quote from: Hasan905 on January 23, 2018, 07:45:07 PM ATTENTION PLEASE  To every one. Manager Aventhy is on Holiday now, He will come back on Sunday and hopefully will solve all your problems. So be patient until next Sunday. He simply told me that you will be informed about this..  Thank you.  Ok, good to know that a Bounty Manager exists, even though he's on a quite long holiday exactly during the time an ICO which aims at collection 40,000,000$ is organized. A quite interesting management of priorities   And here when I have been finally deleted from the spreadsheet:  Quote from: RoccoSiffredi on March 17, 2018, 12:58:08 AM Quote from: DateCoin_support on March 15, 2018, 09:24:19 PM Quote from: disbil on March 15, 2018, 04:59:00 AM Quote from: Asya77 on March 14, 2018, 09:01:46 PM usually such projects like this succeed. people need something for make their brains relax. games also, like this project with different types of cats I think this project has great potential to be successful. and I'm sure if all the team will work hard and work well together, so as to be able to make this project a success. We have a team of professionals. We are striving for success!  I hope your professionals are better than your bounty manager, who has been away for over one month and once back he has apparently deleted my signature campaign stakes, which basically means a certain easiness in stealing the work of collaborators.  Your manager seems to have extended his vacation for another two weeks of more it seems - LoL this campaign starts to really look like a joke, spreadsheet not updated even once in over a month, team not able to keep even its most simple promises like having one manager dealing with the bounties... Together with you, we have passed a long and difficult path of eight months. At the same time, there is still more to be overcome by our team, which has been given such a great credit of trust in the form of millions of investments from thousands of people around the world.  During the preparation and holding of the ICO, we have attracted hundreds of specialists of different profiles, dozens of consultants, prepared dozens of videos and thousands of texts, met with a huge number of investors, gathered in our groups in social networks, without exaggeration, a real crypto army of people who care about the fate of DateCoin.  At the same time, we have faced a lot of problems, the description of which can take several days. We do not give up this experience, as in many ways it helped us to assemble an effective team of real professionals and understand how to develop further and build a multi-million dollar business in order to fulfill the moral obligations to our investors.  We are grateful to all of you for the opportunity to make a revolution in the dating market and prove to the whole crypto community that against the background of growing skepticism towards the ICO in general, it is possible to organize an honest sale of the project tokens and actively develop the project. We're not saying goodbye. From this moment on, a fundamentally new life with new challenges and goals begins for our community. Stay with us and continue to follow the news on our sites. Body: 📌 Revolutionary dating app DateCoin enters Japanese market  Japan is one of the first countries where it will be possible to fully use DateCoin application. DateCoin project team got acquainted with investors and market features of this country in March 2018, within the framework of Teamz business summit, which was held in the capital of Japan-Tokyo. The market research in Japan showed high prospects for the development of the dating industry in the region, which served as the basis for the decision to introduce the application DateCoin to this market.  Before its launch on the market, DateCoin application will be fully adapted for the Japanese user. In order to do this we conducted an in-depth study of the Japanese market, studied the features of the Japanese nation and the principles of marketing in the market. As for today we have already made a full translation, developed and implemented the design, fully assembled the application and launched the text. Now the application is at the stage of improvements. A full launch on the market of Japan in scheduled for July 2018.  In the future plans of our project – there are the launch of the application DateCoin on the markets of 23 countries of the world by 2020. According to the results of our research, the project's paying audience is about 50-60 million people around the world. According to our estimates, DateCoin application claims to be a global leader in the field of dating for wealthy men and beautiful women. By 2021 we are planning to take a leading position in the markets of Asia, Europe and South America with a share of 45-60% in its segment.  ☑️ Join now https://datecoin.io

Body: 📌 DateCoin took part in "Crypto Forum for Hotcoins"  On the 24 of May in Seoul DateCoin team members took part in a large-scale blockchain event called "Crypto Forum for Hotcoins". More than 20 projects (mostly Korean) were presented at the crypto forum. The event was attended by hundreds of people as visitors and dozens of people from various ICO.  From the stage DateCoin was presented by its PR-Director Oleg Gervalov. He was assisted by a project consultant Jay Lee. During his speech, Oleg Gervalov demonstrated the design of Datecoin dating service for South Korea and announced the release of the token at the end of May on three exchanges, including AllCoin and a number of others. According to the PR Director, in June and July the token will be presented at two major exchanges in Korea and Japan.  Team members of DateCoin also actively introduced the visitors of the event to the project within the frameworks of the great exhibition that took place in hotel Le Meridien, where the cryptoforum was held. Many of them received gifts from DateCoin– commemorative coins and t-shirts.  The peculiarity of the crypto forum was its focus directly on the local market and the participation of Korean investors in it. The event was actively covered by the news channel SBS CNBC.  The crypto forum also aimed to acquaint traditional investors with the features of investing in ICO through a detailed analysis of projects. One of the topics was the regulatory impact of the state on the cryptocurrency market in Korea.  https://datecoin.io.

Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: Andromeda Capital and DateCoin have signed a strategic partnership agreement, including $1M investments  Andromeda fund (Switzerland) and DateCoin have signed a strategic partnership agreement. As a part of a deal, the fund has purchased DTC tokens ($1M). The deal was closed 9 days before the end of ICO.  “We have been monitoring DateCoin for several months, emphasized Pavel Kornilov, Andromeda Group Co-Founder.   Today we are glad to announce the start of long-term partnership with DateCoin team. The project possesses convincing business plan and token price rise mechanics implemented.” According to Pavel Kornilov, the project is well-known and differs favourably from the majority of ICOs.  Nikita Anufriev, DateCoin CEO and founder, emphasized the top priority of this partnership. “The investments we got, make us closer to the hard cap, thus accelerating project scaling and expansion. The latter will, for sure,  contribute to the project popularity and ensure the token to be in high demand.   Andromeda Capital is a global investment company which is a part of Andromeda Group, a diversified group of companies active in the decentralized economy.Andromeda focuses on strategic investments into disruptive technologies with long-term fundamental value and invests into companies that have the potential to make economic and social impact in the world  About DateCoin  The founders of DateCoin aim to employ cutting-edge technologies for intelligent dating with your soulmate or at least with a person sharing your interests. DateCoin uses artificial intelligence and big data processing to analyze user preferences, contact history, etc, in order to generate a pool of the best matching partners. Blockchain is used to create a trustworthy environment by solving user identification and verification problems, and the distributed data technology ensures authenticity of each verified account. The project has MVP, online dating service Denim https://mvp.datecoin.io, which is a market leader of dating in Russia.   In future, the token price will be secured by the growing audience worldwide. According to our forecasts, DateCoin will reach a milestone of 20 million app users in upcoming 4 years. Most of them will purchase DTC tokens at the exchange to pay for unique in-app features or to be eligible for special offers. DateCoin is currently holding a public ICO. To join ICO and for more details about DateCoin, please visit https://datecoin.io.

Author: DateCoin_support
Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: One of the most important problems in the field of dating services is a unique identification of users and we know how to solve this problem!  In DateCoin there will be no fake profiles!  Why? Because we will verify all users personally-at a personal meeting.  But how is it possible – ask you, how can you hold millions of meetings with all users in all parts of the world? Answer!  We will transfer the verification process of the questionnaires to the users themselves. That's how it's going to work:  💜 We personally verify some accounts of our users, after which they will receive the "Verified" status.  💜 "Verified" user will be able to confirm the identity of other users at a personal meeting by recording the transaction with all its data in our register of distributed data  💜 After confirmation the second user will also be "Verified" and will be able to confirm other users in private meetings on a date   The essence of the technology of decentralization will not change or correct the signatures of verified users when making entries in the blockchain. Thus, we will not only solve the problem of fake profiles but also protect the service from fraudsters and unscrupulous users.   Why do users pass the verification - you may ask? In fact, everything is simple:  💜 "Verified" user a priori will be more interesting for other DateCoin users  💜 "Verified" user will also be of interest to new members wishing to obtain this status   What do we get in the end?  Honest and transparent dating service where the user will be sure that this nice girl with whom he communicates is exactly that young lady on the photo, not a 120-pound guy named Chuck living in the basement of mom (c).  https://datecoin.io.

Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: A director himself: what makes people from different parts of the world shoot videos about DateCoin?  DateCoin inspires people around the world not only to invest in the project but also to create diverse content to tell as many people as possible about it and its prospects. Representatives of different nations make reviews on different sites, draw pictures, witty memes, shoot videos and make animated cartoons (examples: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NKOgwzCzjxk https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1OOrDCcSAME) and so on.  Our attention was drawn to a video about our project, which was shot by a young man named Sid originally from Bangladesh. This video is not devoid of a certain comic sense and made with humor-its plot boils down to the fact that two cute guys go into a room, where they see two pretty girls and try to impress them with a thick pack of dollar bills, then large coins, thus demonstrating their success. Ladies at the same time show that it doesn’t impress them. They are interested in a modest young man with glasses, hesitantly entering the hall and sitting at the table, on which he pours coins with the logo of DateCoin, which symbolizes the tokens of the project. The girls surround the young man, arousing the outright envy of the other two young men watching the picture.  We have asked Sid a few questions and found out that he has been following the project for a long time and the idea of creating a data service that uses neural networks, big data processing and other technologies seems interesting to him. “All this makes the project different from others — it’s really the technology of the future that can change our lives. And if the project is in demand-it will be profitable. That’s why I decided to record a video of this ICO and upload it to my YouTube channel»  Sid’s YouTube channel is entirely dedicated to ICO and cryptocurrencies. According to him, he studies the market of the most promising projects and watches various video reviews on them. However, he believes, it all seems so “monotonous and boring”.  “That’s why we have decided to add some humor to our review,” Sid explains. — I think that memorable and funny clips can help to promote DateCoin and other projects. Making a video about Datecoin I want to tell about the project and show my peers and friends how important relationships can be for us — when you are young, there is nothing better than profitable projects and beautiful girls! Datecoin combines both! And I would like to thank the creators of the project from the bottom of my heart for the fact that they were able to create such a product. I believe in the success of this coin!»  Sid’s video of the DateCoin project https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d5VCaWCbsRY

Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: Online Dating: blockchain VS bots  In China a real dating scandal is gaining momentum: it turned out that tens of thousands of men were victims of fraud on Dating sites. Bots were able to deceive them. The Chinese entered into correspondence with them, flirted, fell in love and parted with large sums of money. We are talking about a billion yuan, which is about 155 million dollars.  The men who visit dating sites in search of a pair sometimes are generous and giving people. Sometimes it can play with them a cruel (and rather expensive!) joke, as it has happened in China. It all began with the fact that the police received numerous statements from the men of Guangdong province – they all claimed that they were deceived by women with whom they met on dating sites. The beauties ripped off the gentlemen for electronic gifts and offered to buy their photos and videos of erotic content after that they disappeared. Since the complaints were widespread, began the test which showed that there were no women who led sex-correspondence with the naive victims - there were robots. The fraudulent scheme was served by about 600 people, and 21 companies were engaged in the development of software for creating sex bots that could support conversation and interest a man.  The case of China is an example of how artificial intelligence can be used for illegal purposes even within the framework of daiting. The team of the ICO-project DateCoin – the first online dating service with the use of artificial intelligence and neural networks-offers to deal with such phenomena and attackers by their own means, that is, modern technologies.  The problem of so-called "fakes" and bots will be completely solved through the use of blockchain. Thus, a "trusted" user of the service who has such a status will be able to confirm his / her reality at a personal meeting with another user by recording the transaction with all his / her data in our register of distributed data. After such confirmation, the second user will become trusted and thus be able to confirm other users during personal meetings. Thus, it is not just the solution of the problem but the whole ecosystem within the service. The technology of the blockchain will not allow you to replace the individual signature of trusted users during record creation. The openness of the data in the blockchain will make it possible to identify fraudulent actions in relation to the verification of users by other unscrupulous users.  Verification of users using a blockchain is not the only advanced technology that will be used by the team DateCoin.  Details of the project and the ICO which starts on the 30 of March can be found on the website https://datecoin.io

Christmas is completely out of competition — it forces men and women to be interested in representatives of the opposite sex almost twice as often as usual. Body: Sites and Dating applications: how to use artificial intelligence to choose a pair and not to make a mistake?  Ask one thing and choose another. This rule of capricious buyers fully applies to the visitors of dating services. According to the researchers, people in their questionnaires on sites and dating applications indicate those requirements for the partner, which are not really very important for them.  Dating services in the form in which they exist today more often prevent from finding a suitable partner than help to do it. This was shown by a study of American psychologists. They chose 350 men and women who were not too successful regulars of dating sites, who didn’t manage to find a mate. Each of them filled out a voluminous questionnaire, telling in detail about themselves and listing their wishes for their partner. On the basis of these data, scientists compiled a list of successful couples and to “approve” it held an evening of express dating. Each participant of the experiment was able to communicate with 10–12 potential partners, and then listed those who he/she liked most. As a result, some men and women went from experimental party together. Alas, among them there was not a single pair from the list drawn up by psychologists. None of the lovers thought about their wishes and requirements from a previously compiled questionnaire.  One could blame the participants of this experiment for insincerity, but users of sites and dating applications are not always lying deliberately. The stereotypes accepted in society put a lot of pressure on them. “Everyone appreciates blondes 90–60–90. Means, I must like them as well!» — thinks every second man. And in fact, probably, he is not a fond of a cold beauty, but he likes bright eyes, and he doesn’t like a thin waist but adores large breast and stocky build.  This problem can be solved by using the technology of more data processing and intelligent algorithms for fast search and successful dating with ideally-matched partners, so online dating will look absolutely different.  So, for example, DateCoin service will use artificial intelligence for analyzing the texts of dialogs, favorite photos, viewed profiles, the duration of communication with potential partners and the content of dialogs — in other words, all the activity of the user. This significantly increases the probability that a person will really find the most suitable pair, because he won’t be able to distort his real goals and interests by an accident. Whatever a user is looking for — a strong family relationship, a romantic relationship or quick sex — DateCoin will be able to help him, ensuring maximum cybersecurity through symmetric data encryption for the functionality of the dialogs and secure key storage of databases on distributed servers.  DateCoin service will be implemented on the basis of already successful working business model (Denim MVP-application https://datecoin.io/mvp), so that some of its capabilities can be assessed today.  Implementation of a large-scale project using the latest technologies is carried out through the ICO. The Pre-sale of the tokens was successfully completed in December 2017, the Crowdsale will be held in March 2018. You can purchase the tokens and learn more about the project on the website https://datecoin.io  http://cryptoconsulting.info/2018/news/sites-and-dating-applications-how-to-use-artificial-intelligence-to-choose-a-pair-and-not-to-make-a-mistake/

Author: Nikita_Anufriev
Title: [ANN-ICO]💖 DATECOIN 💖🔥THE FASTEST SUCCESSFUL MATCH. THE HOTTEST ICO EVER.🔥💖
Body: Hello, I apologize for your waiting for a response. To be honest I was expecting such a question.  While preparing for iCO, we analyzed the market and came to the conclusion that almost all dating or social networks projects on blockchain  try to solve problems through the blockchain but it can be solved much easier, and in most cases iusing blockchain it is not necessary and is unsubstantiated.  Other similar projects have very little benefit, and also promise unjustified growth of the token.  Therefore, we decided to be as clear as possible and openly use blocking technology to attract financing and implement a reverse buy-back scheme built on a smart contract that will distribute 20% of the company's revenue each month between all the token holders who will decide to participate in the revenue for the period.  Please, be noted that after the token takes part in the distribution of revenue - it will burn, that case will lead to a decrease in the number of tokens in circulation, and as a result, the value of each token increases. Thereby ensuring a constant increase in their value.  Yes - this is not a standard, but fundamentally new approach in the ICO sphere, which is as clear and understandable to investors as possible.  Also I wouldn't hide that we are rely on a rather large amount of investments from the cryptofunds who have already shown interest in the project.  If we talk not about the investment component, but about project's substance, through DateCoin it will be possible to get access to the best girls all over the world, both for the crypto currency and for the internal currency DateCoin.  And we are sure that men need beautiful girls around the world, and crypto-communication is not an exception  Regarding to the second part of the question, we have already invested about 1 million USD in the project, and these funds have already paid off. But even the current yield is not enough to make the project truly international and emplement new technologies. I also want to note that our project is regularly interested in various venture funds, but we decided that raising funds using blockchain technology is the most promising option in the current market conditions.
